<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IPANÉ | Curated Gifts & Baskets</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #fafafa;
            --text-color: #333;
            --accent-color: #d4a373; 
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        h1 {
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-text {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .grid-baskets {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        h3 {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            display: block;
            margin: 25px 0;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            background: var(--text-color);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent-color);
        }

        footer {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #999;
            background: var(--white);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Mobile Adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header { padding: 60px 20px; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>IPANÉ</h1>
        <p class="tagline">The Art of Gifting with Affection</p>
    </header>

    <section id="concept">
        <h2>The "Mimo" Concept</h2>
        <p class="about-text">We don’t just deliver gift baskets. We create curated experiences for those who appreciate the beauty of a genuine gesture and the luxury of fine details.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="shop">
        <div class="grid-baskets">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Small Basket</h3>
                <p>A delicate, thoughtful gesture.</p>
                <span class="price">$65</span>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="border-color: #eee;">
                <h3>Medium Basket</h3>
                <p>Our favorite curation for special moments.</p>
                <span class="price">$110</span>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Large Basket</h3>
                <p>The ultimate luxury IPANÉ experience.</p>
                <span class="price">$180</span>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>Handcrafted in California</p>
        <p>Serving Pleasanton, Livermore & Region</p>
        <br>
        <p>&copy; 2026 IPANÉ. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
